---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy"
  description="A short note on the data practices of ringdove.studio."
>
  <section class="plate doc" data-section="Privacy" data-page="— / VI">
    <article class="inner">
      <header>
        <span class="kicker">A short note</span>
        <h1>On <em>privacy.</em></h1>
      </header>

      <p>
        This site is intentionally quiet about its visitors. It sets no cookies, runs no analytics,
        and ships no third-party scripts. Pages are static; the server logs that any web host keeps
        are the only record of a visit, and we do not read them for marketing purposes.
      </p>

      <p>
        The contact link is a plain <em>mailto:</em> — when you click it, your mail client opens with
        <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a> already in the To field. Nothing is sent until
        you press send. Mail you choose to send sits in our inbox until we have replied and a
        reasonable interval has passed; we keep correspondence we need for the work, and we do not
        share it with anyone outside the studio.
      </p>

      <p>
        If we ever add an analytics service or a contact form, this page will be updated to say so
        plainly, and where appropriate a banner will appear before any tracking begins.
      </p>

      <p class="contact">
        Questions or requests under GDPR can be sent to
        <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>.
      </p>

      <p class="meta">
        Updated <em>April 2026</em>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .plate {
    min-height: calc(100vh - var(--frame-w) * 2);
    padding: 64px 56px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }
  .inner {
    max-width: 56ch;
    width: 100%;
  }
  header {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .kicker {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
    line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  p {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  p :global(em) {
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  a {
    transition: font-style 220ms ease;
  }
  a:hover {
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .contact {
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule-soft);
  }
  .meta {
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .plate {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
